trans-unit.source: The default types in the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter> control.

Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter"></xref> control should show the type browser directly when a user tries to select a type.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePresenter"> </xref> kontrollen skal vise typen nettleseren direkte når en bruker prøver å velge en type.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.View.TypePrensenter> control should show the type browser directly when a user tries to select a type; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
